(248, '[id: jg_cvbuvpqs]\r\n[al:]\r\n[ti:It\'s not goodbye]\r\n[ar:Laura Pausini]\r\n[by:xun]\r\n\r\n[00:19.67]Now what if I never kiss your lips again\r\n[00:24.39]Or feel the touch of your sweet embrace.\r\n[00:28.83]How would I ever go on?\r\n[00:31.93]Without you there\'s no place to belong\r\n[00:37.52]Well someday love is going to lead you back to me\r\n[00:41.71]But till it dose I\'ll have an empty heart\r\n[00:46.02]So I\'ll just have to believe\r\n[00:50.43]Somewhere out there you\'re thinking of me\r\n[00:54.09][02:06.51][02:58.40][03:32.07]Until the day I let you go,\r\n[00:58.22][02:10.23][03:02.59][03:35.29]Until we say our next hello\r\n[01:02.04][02:13.95][03:05.94][03:38.76]It\'s not goodbye.\r\n[01:04.63][02:16.77][03:43.29]Till I see you again\r\n[01:07.41][02:19.58][03:11.91][03:46.42]I\'ll be right here remembering when\r\n[01:11.41][02:23.40][03:15.78][03:48.95]And if time is on our side\r\n[01:15.62][02:27.71][03:20.03][03:52.80]There will be no tears to cry on down the road\r\n[01:21.94][02:34.46][03:26.79][04:00.80]There is one thing I can\'t deny\r\n[01:25.66][02:36.46][02:49.18][03:29.29]It\'s not goodbye\r\n[01:32.10]You\'d think I\'d be strong enough to make it trough\r\n[01:36.23]And rise above when the rain falls down\r\n[01:40.61]But it\'s so hard to be strong\r\n[01:43.86]When you\'ve been missing somebody so long\r\n[01:49.32]It\'s just a matter of time I\'m sure\r\n[01:53.76]But time takes time and I can\'t hold on\r\n[01:58.23]So won\'t you try as hard as you can\r\n[02:01.51]To put my broken hearth together again?\r\n[02:05.67]\r\n[02:44.31]Hey......Yeah.....\r\n[03:08.97]Til I see you again\r\n[04:04.43]It\'s not goodbye....', 1, 0, 1, 495, '2016-07-01 08:54:44', '2016-07-01 08:54:44');
